<%= render 'breadcrumbs' %>
<%= render 'practice_editor_sidenav' %>
<div class="grid-container position-relative">
    <div class="grid-row grid-gap">
        <div class="desktop:grid-col-3 grid-col-auto z-bottom">&nbsp;</div>

        <div id="instructions" class="desktop:grid-col-9 grid-col-12 p0">
        <section class="margin-bottom-1">
          <%= render partial: "shared/messages", locals: {small_text: false} %>
          <h1 class="font-sans-2xl margin-bottom-205 line-height-sans-205">Instructions</h1>
          <h2 class="margin-0 text-normal line-height-36">Please follow these instructions to complete each of the following sections for your practice page.</h2>
        </section>
        <br/>
          <section class="desktop:grid-col-8">
            <h2 class="margin-0 text-bold">What you'll need</h2>
              <div class="">
                <ul class="line-height-sans-6 font-sans-md instructions-list">
                  <li>To create a thorough page, you’ll be asked to share data, images, video, instructions, files, and stories related to your practice.</li>
                  <li>All uploaded files should be displayed in a common file format (.jpg, .jpeg, .png, or .pdf) that is ready to be shown to the public. Images must be less than 32MB.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
          </section>
          <section class="desktop:grid-col-8">
          <h2 class="margin-0 text-bold">PII and PHI policy</h2>
          <div class="">
            <ul class="line-height-sans-6 font-sans-md instructions-list">
              <li>Do not enter Personally Identifiable Information (PII) or Protected Health Information (PHI) for any individual, Veteran, or patient.</li>
              <li><%= link_to "Learn more", pii_phi_information_path, class: 'dm-internal-link' %> about what constitutes PII and PHI.</li>
              <li>If you post PII you must fill out and hold onto
                <%= link_to 'Form 3203', 'https://vaww.rtp.portal.va.gov/DEAN/IE/DOE/10-3203.pdf', target: '_blank', class: 'dm-external-link' %>.</li>
              <li>If you want to upload an image that features a Veteran,
                or text that includes a Veterans name or identifiable information you must have
                <%= link_to 'Form 3203', 'https://vaww.rtp.portal.va.gov/DEAN/IE/DOE/10-3203.pdf', target: '_blank', class: 'dm-external-link' %>.
                Waivers must be filled out with the 'External to VA' check box selected.
              </li>
              <li>If you post PHI on the site you must fill out and hold onto
                <%= link_to 'Form 5345', 'https://vaww.rtp.portal.va.gov/DEAN/IE/DOE/10-5345.pdf', target: '_blank', class: 'dm-external-link' %>.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>
          <section class="desktop:grid-col-8">
            <h2 class="margin-0 text-bold">Formatting and editing</h2>
            <div class="">
              <ul class="line-height-sans-6 font-sans-md instructions-list">
                <li>Ensure your work is accurate, formatted consistently, and as complete as possible before publishing.</li>
                <li>Use sentence case (only capitalizing the first word in titles) and spell out acronyms. Capitalize proper nouns and names.</li>
                <li>You will be able to edit your practice once it’s published.</li>
                <li><%= link_to "View an example", practice_path(ENV.fetch('EXAMPLE_PRACTICE_SLUG', 'project-happen')), class: 'dm-internal-link' %> of a well-formatted completed practice.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

      <div class="grid-row flex-auto margin-bottom-3">
        <div class="bg-gold padding-2 radius-md">
          <p class="text-bold margin-bottom-1">Need help along the way?<p>
          <p>Reach out to a member of our support staff with your question. <a class="dm-banner-link" href="mailto:marketplace@va.gov" target="_blank">Send us an email<i class="margin-left-1 fas fa-external-link-alt text-no-underline"></i></a><p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <%= link_to practice_introduction_path(@practice), class: 'usa-button dm-btn-base pe-continue editor-continue-link margin-right-1 margin-bottom-5' do %>
          Continue
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
